: 202}, {\"ngram\": \"honour\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Three years after narrowly missing out on a medal at Tokyo 2020, the Holywood-born golfer is returning to the Summer Games with hopes of glorious gold.\", \"from\": 258, \"to\": 409, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 300, \"to\": 307}, {\"ngram\": \"Tokyo\", \"from\": 311, \"to\": 316}, {\"ngram\": \"the Holywood-born golfer\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 347}, {\"ngram\": \"the Summer Games\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 380}, {\"ngram\": \"hopes\", \"from\": 386, \"to\": 391}, {\"ngram\": \"glorious gold\", \"from\": 395, \"to\": 408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The men's tournament runs from Thursday and culminates in Sunday's finale when the three medal-winners will be announced in the French capital.\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 553, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 538, \"end\": 544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9852522048431347, \"rank\": 0.005856542979627555, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The men's tournament runs\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 435}, {\"ngram\": \"Thursday\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 449}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday's finale\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 483}, {\"ngram\": \"the three medal-winners\", \"from\": 489, \"to\": 512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Northern Irishman McIlroy will be competing on Ireland's behalf, just as he did during his Olympic debut in Japan three years prior.\", \"from\": 555, \"to\": 696, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 611, \"end\": 618, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9992689156239777, \"rank\": 0.000563052648062579, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 677, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8570863037163535, \"rank\": 0.16180391769117314, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Northern Irishman McIlroy\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic debut\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite being eligible to represent either Ireland or Team GB at the Summer Games, the decision has always been straightforward for the four-time major winner, reportsThe Mirror.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 875, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 740, \"end\": 747, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9992689156239777, \"rank\": 0.000563052648062579, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 751, \"end\": 758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.6555032549372396, \"rank\": 0.5255454358705065, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Summer Games\", \"from\": 762, \"to\": 778}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 780, \"to\": 792}, {\"ngram\": \"the four-time major winner\", \"from\": 829, \"to\": 855}, {\"ngram\": \"reportsThe Mirror\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 874}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McIlroy, 35, has never wavered in his allegiance despite having the unique privilege of choosing between two teams.\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 992, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"McIlroy\", \"from\": 877, \"to\": 884}, {\"ngram\": \"his allegiance\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 925}, {\"ngram\": \"the unique privilege\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"two teams\", \"from\": 982, \"to\": 991}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Just like in Tokyo, the golf icon is eager to bring glory to the Emerald Isle this weekend.\", \"from\": 993, \"to\": 1084, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1006, \"end\": 1011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6028326978668788, \"rank\": 0.6588348802422263, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the golf icon\", \"from\": 1013, \"to\": 1026}, {\"ngram\": \"glory\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1050}, {\"ngram\": \"the Emerald Isle\", \"from\": 1054, \"to\": 1070}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Once I left trying not to upset anyone aside, then it was actually a pretty easy decision,\\\" he said ahead of Tokyo 2020.\", \"from\": 1086, \"to\": 1207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1196, \"end\": 1201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.6028326978668788, \"rank\": 0.6588348802422263, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 1119, \"to\": 1125}, {\"ngram\": \"a pretty easy decision\", \"from\": 1154, \"to\": 1176}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The decision was I am going to play golf for the country or the nation that I have always played for through my junior and amateur days and now into the professional game.\", \"from\": 1208, \"to\": 1380, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The decision\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1221}, {\"ngram\": \"golf\", \"from\": 1245, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"the nation\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"my junior and amateur days\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1344}, {\"ngram\": \"the professional game\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1379}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And that's Ireland.\\\"\", \"from\": 1381, \"to\": 1401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1392, \"end\": 1399, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9992689156239777, \"rank\": 0.000563052648062579, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite the political divide, when it comes to the Olympics, athletes from both Northern Ireland and the Republic of Ireland unite under a single banner.\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1556, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1483, \"end\": 1499, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9753501559485961, \"rank\": 0.025272814999466497, \"text\": \"Northern Ireland\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Northern_Ireland\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the political divide\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1431}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1450, \"to\": 1462}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1464, \"to\": 1472}, {\"ngram\": \"the Republic\", \"from\": 1504, \"to\": 1516}, {\"ngram\": \"Ireland\", \"from\": 1520, \"to\": 1527}, {\"ngram\": \"a single banner\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"McIlroy found himself in a complex situation due to his background but has always represented Ireland in golf.\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1651, \"end\": 1658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9992689156239777, \"rank\": 0.000563052648062579, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpe